es.utils.mapper.factory.builder

Interface To<IN,GETTER_OUT,SETTER_IN,OUT>

  • Type Parameters:
    IN - the type of the origin object
    GETTER_OUT - the resulting type of the getter operation
    SETTER_IN - the input type of the setter operation
    OUT - the type of the destination object
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DefaultInput<IN,GETTER_OUT,SETTER_IN,OUT>, DefaultOutput<IN,GETTER_OUT,SETTER_IN,OUT>, Transformer<IN,GETTER_OUT,SETTER_IN,OUT>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EMBuilder

    public interface To<IN,GETTER_OUT,SETTER_IN,OUT>
    Last step of the EMBuilder (before the building one) that manage the creation of the setter operation.
    This step is mandatory (Consume and To are mutually exclusive) Previous step: DefaultOutput
    Next step: Builder
    Author:
    eschoysman
    See Also:
    builder package
